James C. Leary https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_C._Leary 0 James C. Leary (born August 26, 1973) is an American actor best known for his portrayal of the relatively benign demon Clem who appears in Seasons Six and Seven of the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer.
